      "solution": "import sys\nliste = input()\nlieu = input()\nprint(liste, file=sys.stderr)\nprint(lieu, file=sys.stderr)\n# 0 : Up, 1 : Right, 2 : Down, 3 : Left, 4 : 0.5\nnb = [1, 1, 1, 1, 0.5]\npos = {\"U\" : 0, \"R\" : 1, \"D\" : 2, \"L\" : 3}\npli = {\"U\" : [[4, 4], [1, 1], [0, 2], [3, 3]], \"R\" : [[0, 0], [4, 4], [2, 2], [1, 3]], \"D\" : [[0, 2], [1, 1], [4, 4], [3, 3]], \"L\" : [[0, 0], [1, 3], [2, 2], [4, 4]]}\nfor c in liste :\n    effet = pli[c]\n    new = []\n    for i in range(4) :\n        new.append(nb[effet[i][0]] + nb[effet[i][1]])\n    for i in range(4) :\n        nb[i] = int(new[i])\n    print(c, nb, file=sys.stderr)\nprint(nb[pos[lieu]])",
